rComments: Great Prof. If you go to lectures and take good notes you will get good grades in his course. Very clear when describing what he wants from students. Drops hints throughout the semester on possible final exam questions. Very approachable when a student needs help. I would absolutely take another class with him.

Awesome Professor. Very helpful during office hours. I look forward to any class he teaches. His lectures are very clear and it is easy to understand what is important. Lectures are absolutely mandatory. He provides so much information to the course that is outside of the course readings. He is truly more than qualified. Highly recommend!

I took this course in the summer and I loved it!! His lectures are so interesting. He doesn't really emphasize on the textbook and to be honest I barely did any readings, just took a lot of notes from his lectures and managed to get an A-. Highly recommend it!
Great and interesting lecturer that has a passion for what he is teaching.
